<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/506480-has-anyone-found-this-book-a-bit-tough-to">Has anyone found this book a bit tough to read? I am done with almost 30% of it and I am finding it a bit too tough. Linguistics is not my field at all and maybe that&#39;s the reason.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_506480'><a id="like_count_community_question_506480" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/506480?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">8 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F5755.The_Language_Instinct">like</a></span>

</li>
