<span id="freeTextContainer2255330681091759239">A highly interesting book about how language came about in the human mind. It gets quite technical at times, but that&apos;s an added bonus for anyone who is truly interested in the subject.</span>
  <span id="freeText2255330681091759239" style="display:none">A highly interesting book about how language came about in the human mind. It gets quite technical at times, but that's an added bonus for anyone who is truly interested in the subject.</span>
