      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/2422982-the-language-instinct-how-the-mind-creates-language">Quotes from The Language Inst...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
